class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>) {\n        errorbars.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ClearFormats</span>()\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
